data.description: Two unit grey stone is available for you! This building features a total of 7 bedrooms, 1st fl 3 bed and 2 baths, 2nd fl is 4 bed 2 baths. The basement is the length of the building and partially finished for a possible 3rd unit. Each unit has separate furnaces and water tanks. The back porch is brand new built in 2023, last updated in 2019, the units are turn key and ready to go. Property is being sold AS/IS WHERE IS and shall be rendered vacant. Owners unit and basement will be available for showing, 2nd unit will be available after offer acceptance for inspection. Lay out is very similar, with extra room. Schedule a showing today!! Easy to show
